                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-229" type="given" value="ISSAC"></interp>ISSAC QUINSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 87). I gave information of this—the prisoner said nothing of this sort when he was taken.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420613-name-230" type="witnessName">
