                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> When I apprehended him he said he was going to Paddington.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I said the carter was going to Paddington, not that I was going.<hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> He said he was going to Paddington with his mates, with the two carts and horses.</p>
